Package: pchartr
Title: pchartr is a set of tools for analyzing control charts, specifically
    p-charts.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Matthew", "Grogan", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "mvgnyc@gmail.com"))
Description: This package contains tools for detecting out-of-control conditions
    on control charts using the rules proposed by Lloyd Nelson.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-2
Collate:
    'pchartr-package.r'
    'check_nelson_rules.R'
    'nelson.rule1.R'
    'nelson.rule2.R'
    'nelson.rule3.R'
    'nelson.rule4.R'
    'nelson.rule5.R'
    'nelson.rule6.R'
    'nelson.rule7.R'
    'nelson.rule8.R'
    'plot.nelson_rule.R'
    'print.nelson_rule.R'
    'is.nelson_rule.R'
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 0.2)
